Gummy Drop Smash! (“we,” “our,” or “us”) respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how your personal and technical information is collected, used, and disclosed when you use our mobile game, Gummy Drop Smash! (the “Game”), available on Android.

By accessing or using the Game, you acknowledge this Privacy Policy.

