We do not directly collect personal information such as names, email addresses, phone numbers, payment information, or login credentials. However, third-party services may collect technical identifiers and usage data.

We automatically collect technical and usage data necessary for the operation of the Game and advertising purposes. This may include:

Device information (model, operating system, unique device identifiers)
Country / region (based on IP address, for analytics)
