We do not share personal information directly with advertisers. However, data may be collected and processed by third-party services such as Google AdMob, Google Firebase, and Google Play Console in accordance with their own privacy policies.

These third-party services may process data outside your country of residence.

Users in the European Economic Area (EEA) are shown a consent form for personalized and non-personalized advertising in accordance with GDPR requirements. You can manage or withdraw your consent at any time through your device settings or via the consent management tool provided in the application (if available).

For more information on how Google uses data, please visit: https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads

